    <img class="header_img" src="/images/website-homepage-header_orig.jpg" alt="">
  </header>

  <div class="artists_msg my-4" style="text-align:center; width:85%;">
    <hr><br>
    <h4 class="msg-text">Welcome to TP on Canvas! Free the Me is my movement to put more focus back on myself and put effort into the things that inspire and motivate me. My paintings reflect exactly that. I enjoy acrylic on canvas, bold colors and organic abstract images
      and scenes. Take a look around and find what inspires you. Salud!</h4><br>
    <hr>
  </div>
  <div class="container">

    <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img class="d-block w-100" src="<%= paintings[0].img_location %>" alt="First slide">
        </div>
        <% for(let i = 1; i < paintings.length; i++){ %>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="<%= paintings[i].img_location %>" alt="First slide">
          </div>
          <% } %>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
